Class PopulationTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • db.PopulationTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TableModel

    public class PopulationTableModel
extends AbstractTableModel
    This class used virtualize values stored in the PopulationTable Class. NOTE - This class is necessary in order to make updates (aka CRUD) to the PopulationTable class.
    Author:
    Brady Houseknecht
